name: Jill Howard
description: I consider myself as a very energetic, open and sociable person. I like to communicate with different people. I am goal-oriented and I always know what I want. I set up my goals and do everything to achieve them. Honesty, trust and respect are essential for me in a relationship with different people. I expect people to treat me in a way they are treated by me. I am fair, generous and sympathetic woman. I can be gentle and affectionate with my man. I would also say that I am very sensitive, kind and creative person. I am a very active person and that is why I am always in action. I enjoy spending time with my friends. I see a strong man by my side, a responsible man, who is not afraid of difficulties. It is important for me that my future husband has a strong life position, desire to grow and to develop himself personally and professionally. It would be also essential for me if he were open to making compromises. I need a real man, who appreciates his woman and who knows how to make her happy.
